#GoanFishCurry

One of the things I’ve started to love more since I moved to Mumbai years ago is #SeaFood. #GoanPomfretCurry is one of my favourites. latestPosts.caption:
Experience the soul of Bengal at @raajkutir. 
More than just a boutique hotel, Raajkutir is a graceful tribute to a bygone era. Inspired by traditional Raajbaris, it blends Art Deco elegance with old-world charm — from serene courtyards to the grand Uthon, where a stately Palki takes center stage.

Savor the rich culinary heritage of Bengal at The East India Room, where signature thalis celebrate timeless favorites like chingri malai curry, kosha mangsho, luchi, and rossogolla — each dish thoughtfully crafted and beautifully served.

As dusk settles, the courtyard comes alive with the glow of lanterns and soulful live performances by local artists — best enjoyed with a cup of chai and crisp jhal muri.

End your day at Swig, the hotel’s chic, vintage-style bar, where warm wood tones and crafted cocktails invite you to unwind and linger.

🎥 @amit_dey_photography
